/*  REXX PROGRAM NAME : GUESSNUM                          

    DESCRIPTION       : GUESS THE NUMBER SCRIPT            

                                                            

    AUTHOR            : Jon Higgins                        
                 
*/                                                         
the_number = random(1,10)                                  
say "I'm thinking of a number between 1 and 10, What is it?"
pull the_guess                                             
if the_number = the_guess then                             
    say the_number 'is correct!'                           
else                                                       
    say 'Sorry, my number was: ' the_number                
say 'Bye!'  